I saw this object in the sky and decided to film it with my canon - sorry for the shaky video. the sky was clear while i was filming, too - not a cloud in the sky. 

@1:03 of the original video you can see the object is moving right to left - i made this the thumbnail for the video - this happened as i was filming in the tree limb line - you can clearly see it moving or floating right to left. 

in the video you can see a jet's chemtrail flying above this object in a couple of shots. leave a comment if you know what this object is - thanks.
